snippet.textDisplay:
:: "Lalon" songs aren't about the instruments.
No need to overdo everything. Keep it simple. Those rappers are good in other songs, but in this song they seem like they are lost. No need to give everyone their "solo moment".  Sumi has a beautiful, powerful voice. Sad but true She couldn't even shine like her unique performances. Very disappointing music composition. Coke Studio Bangla could represent our music taste, an eccentric Bangladeshi style. But it's just a "super lite" version of Coke studio Pakistan. 😞 CS-pak adding rappers/DJ/rhymes, it doesn't mean we have to copy them word by word.
